          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-pink-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
